<li id="cite_note-61"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-61">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFBirchall2004" class="citation book cs1">Birchall, Ian (2004). <i>Sartre Against Stalinism</i>. <a href="/wiki/Berghahn_Books" title="Berghahn Books">Berghahn Books</a>. p.&#160;29. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-1571815422" title="Special:BookSources/978-1571815422"><bdi>978-1571815422</bdi></a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Sartre+Against+Stalinism&amp;rft.pages=29&amp;rft.pub=Berghahn+Books&amp;rft.date=2004&amp;rft.isbn=978-1571815422&amp;rft.aulast=Birchall&amp;rft.aufirst=Ian&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AAnarchist+communism" class="Z3988"></span></span>
